        "description": {
            "value": "<p>This set of healer's tools contains a seemingly endless supply of bandages, herbs, and healing items of impeccable quality, granting you a +3 item bonus to Medicine checks.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"pf2-icon\">A</span> Treat Poison or 8 hours (Treat Disease)</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You can activate the tools when you use them to Treat Poison in order to produce the effects of a 6th-level <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Neutralize Poison]{Neutralize Poison}</em>, or when you Treat Disease in order to produce the effects of a 6th-level <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Remove Disease]{Remove Disease}</em>.</p>\n<p>Once these medicines have been used to treat a patient's poison or disease, they can't be used again to treat the same affliction for that patient.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Automatically applied effects:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>+3 item bonus to Medicine checks.</li>\n</ul>"
